Project Flow: 
0. Scraper -> CSV of Recipes
1. Pre-Processing -> Filtered Recipe CSV 
2. Allergy Filtration -> Filtered Recipe CSV
3. Ingredient Labeling & Attribute Extraction -> Ingredient List & Attribute List
4. Ingredient Recommender -> Threshold-Filtered Recipe CSV
5. Attribute Recommender -> Sentiment & Similarity Evaluations
6. Final Recommendation -> Top 3 Recipes


Presentation Outline
1. Section 1: Proof of Concept
- Labeling Ingredients Example
- User Description Example
- Recommended Recipes (No Code just Demonstration)
2. Section 2: Backend Workflow
- Scraping
- Pre-Processing
- Allergy Filtration
- Image Analytics & Attribute Extraction (User interaction point)
- Ingredient-Requirements Recommendations
- Attribute-Review Recommendations
3. Section 3: Future Work
- App Design & Chatbot UI
- Memory Features (Allergies, Cookware, Preferences)
- Integration with Grocery Stores (HEB Plugin)